{"tid":1697960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人真係好無賴，博同情打國際戰線","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:55:47.000Z","uid":237435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7853d8da0bd6a72bf72a7a77bc0e4c0540c368","tid":1697960,"uid":237435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"琴日睇到呢個po<br />\n<br />\n有無人支持下呢位正被蝗蟲攻擊的韓國文宣手足(藝人)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁就去佢ig食下花生啦，本身就勁多中国人各自屌鳩佢，佢都有反駁下咁。跟住啲中國人開始sd同一個韓文msg鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都是撚但啦。但之後就黎料啦<br />\n<br />\n佢再po左兩個story，係分別有兩個中国人懶同情打左篇文比佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2J7h0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2J7h0s.png&h=e5596696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「oppa, 我係中國website見到你嘅新聞，因為好擔心你所以黎ig搵你。其實你冇做錯，近排對中國人黎講，香港呢個詞語真係好敏感...廢話省略...但係oppa你應該唔知，香港真係做緊啲我地理解唔到嘅事，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦都比左我地(支那人）好多傷害</span>，所以希望你可以理解我地支那人，oppa你都唔好再發表有關呢件事嘅野啦...因為除左支那人，仲有好多其他人會關注你嘅反應㗎嘛」<br />\n<br />\n個韓國人係呢個story到仲話: <span style=\"color: red;\">誤會左你真係唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRMpko7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRMpko7.png&h=c28db62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個支那人<br />\n「呢件事係其他國家嘅政治問題，韓國人唔係咁清楚㗎嘛，亦都關聯到歷史問題，好複雜，唔該唔好隨便判斷。我都係支那人，我都好愛韓國，但我亦唔會隨便評論韓國嘅政治問題。同埋你唔係一般人，係藝人，係中國都有好多fans，你咁做都會傷害到fans嘅心 (玻璃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)...廢話(討好翻人)...我都係希望世界和平嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n屌 啲中國人真係無賴到一個點，我地要打好啲國際戰線！尤其係啲有影響力嘅藝人，咪比支那狗帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03b47c7ef0871ab6c5a5367f85bdc8c17334c61","tid":1697960,"uid":237435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"今晚Sogo要人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697694</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2c4d60e1cd8f2bd4278e2c9f2fa49eb4e8e10c8","tid":1697960,"uid":237435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xosDpTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxosDpTo.jpg&h=4072085c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73e8b6b092dd5eaedf6d5e6d28ee809d02370a6f","tid":1697960,"uid":170793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"啱 咁點同呢位oppa講   首先要守好呢條戰線"},{"pid":"1b20c564c7fa9b73590865df231fd55a4bf3b9bb","tid":1697960,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c4d60e1cd8f2bd4278e2c9f2fa49eb4e8e10c8","tid":1697960,"uid":237435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xosDpTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxosDpTo.jpg&h=4072085c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"呢個日程表唔夠齊 唔好傳"}]}